  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA12">
<l>nīyaṉṟē yāḻtuyaril vīḻvippā ṉiṉṟuḻaṉṟāy</l>
<l>pōyoṉṟu colliyeṉ pōneñcē nīyeṉṟuṅ</l>
<l>kāḻttupatē cantariṉuṅ kaikoḷḷāy kaṇṇaṉṟāḷ</l>
<l>vāḻttuvatē kaṇṭāy vaḻakku.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is it not that you have constantly suffered to be thrown down into weeping affliction?</l>
<l>What of going [and] saying anything? Go, heart? Even if instruction is given,</l>
<l>you always take it firmly in hand. Praising</l>
<l>the feet of Kaṇṇaṉ, see, is the [right] practice.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
